{"tid":1776410,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"唔準再互屌","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:43:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-09T14:51:42.000Z","uid":317431,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1520c322b98b94db9019919f0bff294c00e90a8b","tid":1776410,"uid":317431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:43:42.000Z","msg":"只要一日還未有五大訴求，我地依然受制被不公義既政權，包括中共、政府、立法會、法院、警察等等機構，因此無論和定勇；泛民定本土，所有受害者要一齊手指向外面，指返去問題既源頭&mdash;唔完善既制度。<br />\n畢竟我地就一齊左六個月，哩段時間令我地更了解彼此既弱點，亦都試過大大小小既爭執。如果有時光機，我希望可以返去好似六個月前既今日咁團結。我地依家不如將錯過既野改正，再做好啲啲，直至實現晒五大訴求。一齊見證2020同2022年普選。那，唔準再互屌喇，好唔好？"},{"pid":"de97a881c52d8dc760c6671caf032808330dfa7c","tid":1776410,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:44:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f052b4e4f4099360fc3573de518f1608451ea77","tid":1776410,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:44:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n昨日遊行最深刻的一句「初夏&mdash;&mdash;寒冬」<br />\n我們不經不覺由初夏走到冬天<br />\n由撐黃色食店走到黃色經濟圈<br />\n香港人就是有心有力也有財力<br />\n<br />\n講返正題，以往每年聖誕聯歡/Re-U都總係會叫啲最方便快捷嘅KFC、PizzaHut聖誕套餐，今年相信大家都不了不了，所以我地整合左所有會做到會服務嘅黃店，大家識Do啦！<br />\n*（亦建議學生會將圖印出派比同學宣傳📃）<br />\n<br />\n最後，教育同行全體祝大家有個Yellow Christmas 🎄💛<br />\n<br />\n*我地已盡量向店方直接確認到會服務，但始終人手有限，資料未必齊全，歡迎各位Comment報料。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nTg: <a href=\"https://t.me/hkteacher\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkteacher&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=67c83280\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkteacher</a><br />\nFb: shorturl.at/kqtJM<br />\nIg: <a href=\"https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fstandbyeducatorshk%3Figshid%3Djuzv8s7rtxb5&d=qnVsOlgekcepRBzFpIlw%2F0YD92OErucUe%2F0sHRi%2FZkY%3D&h=9c33ef58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/standbyeducatorshk?igshid=juzv8s7rtxb5</a>"},{"pid":"d67bcf9e052619b674bc1da828f24b5cdb47fa68","tid":1776410,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kucMp8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkucMp8c.png&h=33c96d8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ee554aa0d3653f5ad3620b9df3a8f5bf348c0af3","tid":1776410,"uid":218731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:59:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bbd1c6412aac37cd507ba6556143544c5b2fabc","tid":1776410,"uid":50414,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:59:24.000Z","msg":"同意"},{"pid":"fe9db224384a7f14e3d49f309bb5e822867a0bdd","tid":1776410,"uid":127553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:00:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UmKV2z6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUmKV2z6.jpg&h=241aee25&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有班教育界痴線佬為左唔比學生落入聖誕節圈套<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1776399\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1776399</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"33b403d1629650e01d14448244cb3696cc2744c3","tid":1776410,"uid":317431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T14:31:16.000Z","msg":"推！我要帶風向"},{"pid":"721c1ebf20f6fd211d36ffda86264204ef533f70","tid":17